1
00:00:01,960 --> 00:00:06,000
National Radio and Television Administration.

2
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:42,600
Wait, you had the child examined?

3
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:44,479
What's wrong with you?

4
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:46,280
Who told you to have the child examined?

5
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:48,080
Look, if you're angry, take it out on me.

6
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:49,440
If anything happens to the child,

7
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,640
I won't let this go, Huaming.

8
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:50,920
Stop arguing.

9
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:51,979
Get out of here now.

10
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:57,080
Hello.

11
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,920
I'm the child's mother.

12
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,320
How is my child doing now?

13
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:02,530
The child has viral encephalitis.

14
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:05,840
Fortunately, his father brought him in time.

15
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:08,440
Otherwise, something terrible could have happened.

16
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:11,100
The child is fine now, so don't be upset anymore.

17
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,620
It's okay, baby. Everything's fine now.

18
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:29,370
I'm quite busy right now

19
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:31,079
with surgeries and stuff.

20
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,440
Okay.

21
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,200
You can go ahead then.

22
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:37,320
Huaming.

23
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,680
Senior Chen Weiming.

24
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,560
What are you doing here?

25
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,890
I work at this hospital.

26
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:44,720
It's been three or four years.

27
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:46,650
Which hospital are you working at?

28
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:49,740
Why are you here today?

29
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,840
Accompanying a friend to see a doctor.

30
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,600
Senior, our phone numbers haven't changed.

31
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,360
I need to take care of something, so I'll go first.

32
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:55,720
Sure.

33
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,930
Let's keep in touch.

34
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,970
Oh my goodness! Thank heavens!

35
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,160
The child has been brought back.

36
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:12,890
Take it easy.

37
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,520
That man today

38
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,520
rushed in and took the child away.

39
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,980
I tried everything to stop him but couldn't.

40
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,610
I know what happened. It's not your fault.

41
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,720
Why would that man take the child?

42
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:27,130
The baby was sick. He took the baby to see a doctor.

43
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:29,720
Xiaomei, keep a close eye on him these days.

44
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,320
If there's anything unusual,

45
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,520
call me immediately.

46
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,560
If you're unsure about anything,

47
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,560
you can also ask the uncle next door.

48
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:41,570
From what you're saying, that man is actually a good person.

49
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:44,420
Alright, I understand. Don't worry.

50
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:46,200
Put him to bed then.

51
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,840
Did you have the child complete the examination?

52
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,680
What's going on with you?

53
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:11,160
Who told you to examine the child?

54
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,920
Leave now. Go!

55
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,240
Mr. Shi, everyone is here now.

56
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,640
Can we start the meeting?

57
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,140
Why isn't Wan Xinxin here?

58
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,360
This Wan Xinxin,

59
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,960
she's always so unreliable.

60
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:08,320
Wan Xinxin is not our employee yet.

61
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:11,360
In a way, she's our partner.

62
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:14,080
We have no right to talk about her like that.

63
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:17,730
Come on, let's first look at the client's requirements.

64
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,640
Hey, Lu Beibei.

65
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:41,080
No.

66
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:43,200
Oh no! Why didn't my alarm go off?

67
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:45,560
Is the dragon lady there yet?

68
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,409
Can you cover for me?

69
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:48,850
I'll be right there.

70
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,880
Please, please cover for me.

71
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,850
Don't let the dragon lady find out.

72
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,770
Hello, this is Hua Ming.

73
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,420
I wanted to discuss with you about

74
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,880
the medical consultation website.

75
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:02,520
I can add ten more slots to my quota.

76
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,520
Yes.

77
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:06,420
Ten more slots on the weekend.

78
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,400
They can still be free of charge.

79
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,660
No problem. It's more convenient for them this way.

80
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:13,330
Goodbye. Thank you.

81
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,340
Xiaomei, please comfort him.

82
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:26,160
Did you hear the alarm just now?

83
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:26,880
Yes, I did.

84
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,220
Then why didn't you wake me up?

85
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:30,640
I'm not a rooster.

86
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:36,540
The house is such a mess. Couldn't you clean up a bit?

87
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:37,640
Listen.

88
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:40,880
We had an agreement before.

89
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:44,060
I'm a nanny, not a housekeeper for the whole family.

90
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:46,159
Besides, you promised yesterday

91
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:47,600
to advance me 1,500 yuan.

92
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,930
I haven't seen any of it.

93
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:51,240
Didn't I tell you already?

94
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,040
I'll pay you after three days.

95
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:55,370
Right now it's a probation period, right?

96
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:56,800
I came to your home

97
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:59,360
haven't seen a penny for taking care of your child,

98
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:01,290
and now you want me to serve you too?

99
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,480
If you do a good job,

100
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,540
you'll get every cent of your salary.

101
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,840
Baby, mommy's leaving now.

102
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,860
Driver, Future Building, hurry!

103
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,320
Oh no!

104
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:24,180
Driver, go back to where we just were!

105
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:34,160
Why are you back, sis?

106
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,580
No. What are you doing?

107
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,450
He's crying so much.

108
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:43,140
Why aren't you taking care of him?

109
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:47,800
His diaper is wet. Go get a new one.

110
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:48,720
Okay.

111
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,970
Mommy will change your diaper.

112
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:01,280
The clothes fit you well.

113
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,880
I feel like I'm the nanny now.

114
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:05,200
And you're acting like the employer.

115
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,120
I'm paying you to work here.

116
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,780
Are we playing role reversal?

117
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:08,520
Listen.

118
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,880
Why are you getting so angry?

119
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,240
Even if I am a nanny,

120
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,600
I still have my dignity.

121
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,640
I suggest you be more polite.

122
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,920
Don't be so rude.

123
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,800
I'm being rude?

124
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:23,360
Did you ask permission to wear my clothes?

125
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,560
Who's being rude now?

126
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:26,000
Do you want this job or not?

127
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,000
I do want the job.

128
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:29,160
But first, pay me what you owe.

129
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,890
And apologize, then I'll work.

130
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,540
What are you thinking?

131
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:35,080
Me, apologize to you?

132
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:36,440
You won't do it?

133
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,800
Fine. I quit.

134
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:41,120
You're quitting?

135
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:43,120
You signed a contract, you know.

136
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:46,920
I came here to earn money, not to be insulted.

137
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:49,240
There's a shortage of nannies now.

138
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,280
Demand exceeds supply.

139
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:52,000
It's very easy to find another job.

140
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,680
With your conditions and attitude,

141
00:10:53,680 --> 00:10:54,680
who would want to work for you?

142
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:55,720
No. With your behavior,

143
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,360
would anyone dare to hire you?

144
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,600
You did, didn't you?

145
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:01,930
Hand it over.

146
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:03,280
What?

147
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,280
The money.

148
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,160
My wages for these two days

149
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:09,560
according to labor law, you laid me off,

150
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:10,760
it wasn't me who quit,

151
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:12,480
you need to pay me double.

152
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,770
You dare talk to me about labor law?

153
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:15,560
Let me tell you,

154
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:17,440
I'm being nice by not calling the police on you.

155
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,520
What did you say?

156
00:11:19,040 --> 00:11:21,240
You're threatening to call the police?

157
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:23,640
I haven't even reported you for withholding migrant workers' wages.

158
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:24,360
You know what?

159
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,020
I'll post this on social media

160
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:27,720
and see who people condemn.

161
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:30,440
How can you be so unreasonable?

162
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:33,000
Hey, what are you doing?

163
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:35,200
Put that down! Those are my clothes! Give them back!

164
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,600
Wait! What are you doing?

165
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:39,720
These two pieces of clothing will cover my wages.

166
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,250
Goodbye.

167
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,440
Come back here!

168
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,970
That's my limited edition!

169
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:48,520
Xiaomei, stop right there!

170
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:51,720
I mean you, not Xiaomei. You can't leave.

171
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:54,200
Fine, I'll give you my limited edition clothes.

172
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:56,800
Okay? Please go back and take care of the child.

173
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:58,760
No! What's wrong with you?

174
00:11:58,760 --> 00:11:59,280
Let me tell you.

175
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:01,640
I've never begged anyone even when I was dating.

176
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:03,040
I'm begging you, please.

177
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,460
I'll pay you. I'll pay you.

178
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:07,160
Money isn't everything.

179
00:12:09,880 --> 00:12:13,680
But having no one to take care of the child is absolutely impossible!

180
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:15,200
Yes, yes.

181
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:17,120
Definitely not acceptable.

182
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:20,640
Mister,

183
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:23,440
why aren't you at work today?

184
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:28,940
The pet hospital is closed for reorganization. I'm off for a few days.

185
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:32,440
So you're free now?

186
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:37,400
I was really wrong yesterday.

187
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:38,800
I was too impatient.

188
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:40,320
You need to understand me.

189
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,400
But as a mother, I'm telling you,

190
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:43,000
we're extremely sensitive.

191
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:46,040
I misunderstood you then. I'm sorry.

192
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,320
You don't need to say more.

193
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,520
I understand what you mean.

194
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:49,600
If you're not afraid I'll

195
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:51,120
sell your child to your ex-husband,

196
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,450
I can watch him for a day.

197
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:55,640
Mister, you really are...

198
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:58,200
You can see right through me

199
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,680
and know exactly what I'm thinking.

200
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:00,520
You know what?

201
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:02,680
You're absolutely my hero right now.

202
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:03,520
Do you realize?

203
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:05,520
Don't worry. I won't have you work for free.

204
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:06,480
I'll pay you.

205
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,880
Pay me? With what?

206
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,000
You haven't even earned any money yourself.

207
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,280
If I'm not mistaken, check your watch.

208
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:11,480
You're already late.

209
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:16,770
Well then, I'll trouble you with this.

210
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:17,840
Baby,

211
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,450
stay with him

212
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:20,680
at home.

213
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:22,240
His diapers and formula

214
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:22,960
are all on the sofa.

215
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,080
You're giving me your keys?

216
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,400
Take everything.

217
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:27,040
I've given you my son, why wouldn't I give you this?

218
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:29,400
Son, have a good day with this mister.

219
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:30,800
Thank you so much!

220
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:34,960
I'll definitely take better care of you than your mom did.

221
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,090
Well, I'm going now.

222
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:37,570
Bye-bye.

223
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,440
Thank you.

224
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:40,280
Wait, what are you doing?

225
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:41,570
Just saying thanks.

226
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:47,920
The biggest challenge for toy brands is the numerous categories.

227
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:50,380
The target audience isn't clearly defined.

228
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,600
According to the client's requirements...

229
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:55,200
Our biggest challenge is the short timeframe.

230
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:58,320
This type of promotion requires planning, performances,

231
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:00,640
and coordination of venues and equipment.

232
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:02,170
With such a tight schedule,

233
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:03,820
won't it be difficult?

234
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:09,000
The greater the challenge, the better we can showcase our capabilities.

235
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,400
If everything were easy,

236
00:14:10,640 --> 00:14:12,160
what would they need us for?

237
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:13,920
Then we need to make the most of our time.

238
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:15,320
Let's get started early.

239
00:14:15,640 --> 00:14:18,360
That's why I'm considering getting involved early.

240
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,240
But Mr. Shi,

241
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,680
we haven't finalized the contract yet.

242
00:14:21,680 --> 00:14:23,140
Advancing funds like this

243
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:25,280
isn't the risk too high?

244
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:27,210
I've already done my research.

245
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:29,640
The client is a financially strong company

246
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:31,850
with a large annual promotion budget.

247
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:34,200
So time is both our problem

248
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,480
and their problem too.

249
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:39,320
I don't care how much money we make from this event.

250
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:42,720
I only care if we can use this promotion

251
00:14:43,280 --> 00:14:45,210
to show them what we're capable of.

252
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:48,880
Mr. Shi, this client is Wan Xinxin.

253
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:50,080
She's responsible for communication

254
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:52,740
and is fully in charge of organizing this event.

255
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:54,200
Can we completely trust

256
00:14:58,280 --> 00:14:59,800
her abilities?

257
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:04,480
Wan Xinxin.

258
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:09,440
Mr. Shi, you look beautiful today.

259
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:11,640
Please continue.

260
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:15,000
I'm late today.

261
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:22,320
No, let me explain. I wasn't supposed to

262
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:23,600
be late at all today.

263
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,640
Actually, I was supposed

264
00:15:24,640 --> 00:15:26,040
to leave half an hour earlier.

265
00:15:26,040 --> 00:15:28,000
But my child was acting up

266
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,440
and then the babysitter was unreliable.

267
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,560
I finally managed to find a neighbor

268
00:15:30,560 --> 00:15:31,680
to watch my child.

269
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:34,120
But that's not the main issue.

270
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:35,640
The real problem was the terrible traffic today.

271
00:15:35,640 --> 00:15:36,640
On the Third Ring Road, you have no idea,

272
00:15:36,640 --> 00:15:38,840
it was all stop and go,

273
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:41,040
and finally my car rear-ended someone,

274
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:42,680
actually hit several cars.

275
00:15:43,920 --> 00:15:44,960
The police came.

276
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:46,720
The driver had to give a statement.

277
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:47,400
I thought...

278
00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:49,080
